	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_idea.gif" alt=":idea:" title="Idea" /><br />I want to play on the network. Not Conter strike or Quake, but Mario.<br />Nothing like that is not for retro gamers.<br /><br />It's a promising idea, to combine many retro - players<br /><br />one way<br />Write the code from scratch or modify disassembler.<br />Write the code for the server.<br /><br />The second path.<br />Special emulator to paint over the image. Such as Lua script. But we need more network functions, which are not. And the server.<br />In this case, players will be able to see each other, but they can not interact.<br />This path easier.<br /><br />What do you think about this?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
